I have to say being a big fan of janet jackson. This was a horribly made video and a cheap way for someone to make a dollar. This video was made poorly and was an insult. If you are a janet fan you will already know all this information. Dont waste your time buying this product.

I do not believe this information is worthy of being deemed "Exposed".  If you are a true fan of Janet Jackson, you have already heard every single thing that is narrated in this video.  It is basically a summary of all the rumors and obvious statements that have already been highlighted over her years of fame.  Also pay attention that this is an "unauthorized" biography so, you will not hear a single note of her music throughout the film, nor will she be present to confirm or deny any of the statements.  The movie, though purchased new, had very poor sound quality and digital distortion as well.  I think this film could have definitely been more professional than what it is.
